    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is a purist's specification featuring the high-revving S65 V8, which utilizes eight individual throttle bodies to deliver a linear power band up to its 8,400 RPM redline. The structural integrity is highlighted by the factory carbon-fiber roof, lowering the center of gravity for enhanced lateral dynamics. Mechanically, the vehicle is robust; the rod bearings and throttle actuators\u2014critical wear items for this platform\u2014have been proactively addressed. The M Variable Differential Lock and EDC (Electronic Damping Control) remain fully functional, providing exceptional turn-in response and mid-corner stability. A well-sorted example of the last naturally aspirated M3, exhibiting crisp gear synchronization and a clean underbody.",
      "price": 34500.0,
